%2F6871928385e81483682de901%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaking%20the%20pasta%20dough.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20made%20a%20well%20in%20our%20pile%20of%20%26quot%3B00%26quot%3B%20flour%20and%20cracked%20each%20egg%20in%20the%20middle%2C%20using%20a%20fork%20to%20break%20up%20the%20yolks%20as%20we%20created%20our%20dough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20kneading%20and%20rolling%20out%20our%20dough%20by%20hand%2C%20we%20made%20our%20first%20pasta%20shape.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Making%20homemade%20pasta%20at%20Florence%20pasta%20class%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687192c585e81483682de90c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaking%20the%20tortelli%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20glass%20of%20red%20wine.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20dish%20was%20tortelli%2C%20a%20stuffed%20pasta%20that's%20a%20bit%20larger%20in%20size%20than%20tortellini.%20Per%20Strazzulo's%20instructions%2C%20I%20carefully%20scooped%20small%20balls%20of%20my%20cheese%20mixture%20to%20dot%20across%20the%20blanket%20of%20dough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20worked%2C%20Strazzulo%20filled%20our%20glasses%20with%20a%20delicious%20Tuscan%20red.%20Did%20I%20mention%20this%20class%20included%20bottomless%20wine%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20make%20the%20homemade%20pasta.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Making%20homemade%20pasta%20at%20Florence%20pasta%20class%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687192e03d5881a51c1d3a25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20used%20a%20pasta%20cutter%20to%20shape%20the%20tortelli.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstan