sinessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-to-italy-for-work-now-back-in-us-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EItaly%3C%2Fa%3E%20trip.%20It%20included%20everything%20you%20could%20want%20from%20Florence%20%E2%80%94%20restaurants%2C%20wine%20tours%2C%20cheese%20and%20sandwich%20shops%2C%20gelato%2C%20and%20cocktails%2C%20as%20well%20as%20additional%20tips%20for%20those%20traveling%20to%20Milan%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-crowds-rome-italy-tips-local-tour-guide%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERome%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20Bologna%20afterward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20night%2C%20we%20used%20the%20list%20to%20find%20a%20pizza%20spot%20and%20had%20a%20lovely%20dinner%20at%20Il%20Pizzaiuolo%2C%20which%20had%20one%20of%20the%20best%20gnocchi%20dishes%20I've%20ever%20tasted.%20The%20list%20also%20directed%20us%20to%20Locale%2C%20a%20chic%20and%20creative%20cocktail%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20first%20dish%20was%20the%20tortelli%2C%20served%20with%20a%20sauce%20of%20brown%20butter%20and%20sage.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Homemade%20ravioli%20at%20Florence%20pasta%20class%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68719336f748d8c055f58266%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20tortelli%20with%20brown%20butter%20and%20sage.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sauce%20couldn't%20be%20easier.%20Strazzulo%20infused%20the%20butter%20with%20sage%20and%20garlic%20cloves%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20melt%20and%20bubble%20until%20it%20browned.%20He%20cooked%20the%20tortelli%20in%20a%20separate%20pot%2C%20adding%20some%20pasta%20water%20to%20our%20brown-butter%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20when%20we%20learned%20a%20secret%20to%20Italian%20cuisine.%20Strazzulo%20finished%20cooking%20the%20pasta%20in%20the%20pan%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20absorb%20more%