0from%20Florence%20pasta-making%20class%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687191c73d5881a51c1d39ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20tagliatelle%20rag%C3%B9%20with%20some%20Parmigiano%20Reggiano%20cheese.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20the%20previous%20two%20dishes%2C%20Strazzulo%20finished%20cooking%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgordon-ramsay-sausage-tagliatelle-pasta-bolognese-recipe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etagliatelle%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20rag%C3%B9%20sauce.%20The%20shower%20of%20Parmigiano%20Reggiano%20cheese%20arrived%20once%20it%20was%20off%20the%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETagliatelle%20is%20my%20favorite%20pasta%20shape%2C%20and%20the%20homemade%20ribbons%20were%20the%20perfect%20vehicle%20for%20the%20rich%20rag%C3%B9%20sauce%20filled%20with%20tender%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20and%20I%20spent%20two-and-a-half%20weeks%20in%20Europe%2C%20and%20this%20remained%20in%20our%20top%20three%20dishes%20of%20the%20entire%20trip.%20We%20walked%20out%20of%20Pasta%20Class%20Florence%20very%20happy%2C%20very%20stuffed%2C%20and%20very%20excited%20to%20try%20the%20recipes%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20lesson%20of%20the%20day%2C%20though%2C%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20pasta.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20best%20meal%20is%20waiting%20in%20the%20most%20unexpected%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-italy-meal-pasta-class-florence-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753185241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6876bb4ef748d8c055f5ab52%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-italy-meal-pasta-class-florence-2025-7%22%2C%22summa