ng%20it%20won't%20work%20in%20this%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoardman%20said%20that%20feedback%20is%20welcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20happens%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20that%20NATO%20best%20practices%20and%20the%20Ukrainians'%20direct%20combat%20experience%20get%20combined.%20There%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Breally%20rich%20mutual%20understanding%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20training%20ultimately%20%26quot%3Bends%20up%20with%20the%20sum%20being%20much%20greater%20than%20the%20parts%2C%20which%20is%20really%20valuable%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoardman%20said%20that%20even%20though%20the%20UK%20has%20%26quot%3Bspent%2020%20or%20so%20years%20in%20the%20counterinsurgency%20focus%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20training%20for%20Ukrainians%20is%20largely%20similar%20to%20what%20is%20given%20to%20the%20UK's%20own%20basic%20recruits%2C%20just%20with%20some%20specific%20focuses%20tailored%20to%20their%20war%2C%20like%20mines%2C%20drone%20warfare%2C%20and%20electronic%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20probably%20teach%20them%20more%20than%20we%20would%20teach%20our%20British%20Army%20recruits%20because%20our%20British%20Army%20recruits%20don't%20go%20straight%20to%20war%20off%20the%20back%20of%20their%20basic%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoardman%20said%20the%20UK%20and%20its%20allies%20benefit%20from%20training%20Ukrainians%20too%2C%20getting%20direct%20feedback%20about%20how%20to%20fight%20Russia%20for%20their%20soldiers.%20He%20said%20trainers%20are%20%26quot%3Blearning%20a%20lot%20from%20the%20Ukrainians%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20also%20feeding%20all%20that%20knowledge%20into%20the%20British%20Army.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20soldiers%20take%20part%20in%20a%20training%20excercise%20operated%20by%20Britain's%20armed%20forces%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Interflex%20programme%2C%20in%20eastern%20England%2C%20on%20February%2024%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%2