y%20at%20used%20book%20sales.%20As%20a%20veteran%20volunteer%20at%20a%20charitable%20used%20book%20sale%2C%20I%20have%20two%20key%20pieces%20of%20advice%3A%20because%20used%20book%20sales%20receive%20so%20many%20children's%20books%2C%20the%20cost%20is%20often%20low%2C%20like%20three%20books%20for%20%241%20for%20paperbacks%2C%20and%20%241%20for%20hardcovers.%20And%20most%20of%20those%20books%20look%20fresh%20off%20the%20bookstore%20shelf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsed%20book%20sales%20can%20be%20found%20everywhere%2C%20from%20libraries%20to%20schools%20to%20houses%20of%20worship.%20You%20can%20track%20down%20sales%20in%20your%20area%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.booksalefinder.com%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBook%20Sale%20Finder%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20have%20a%20successful%20shopping%20trip%2C%20familiarize%20yourself%20with%20payment%20options%20(many%20are%20cash%20only).%20The%20first%20day%20will%20naturally%20have%20the%20largest%20assortment%2C%20but%20it%20will%20also%20likely%20be%20the%20most%20crowded%20and%20may%20not%20be%20the%20best%20time%20to%20bring%20a%20younger%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20sales%20offer%20a%20%26quot%3Bbag%20sale%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20a%20sale.%20You%20pay%20a%20certain%20amount%2C%20often%20about%20%245%2C%20and%20receive%20a%20bag%20you%20can%20fill%20for%20that%20price.%20Depending%20on%20the%20size%20of%20your%20books%2C%20you%20could%20end%20up%20with%20dozens.%20Even%20if%20you%20went%20to%20the%20sale%20earlier%2C%20take%20a%20chance%20on%20a%20second%20visit%20for%20the%20bag%20sale%20if%20there%20is%20a%20large%20assortment%20of%20children's%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwallet-friendly-shopping-tips-stay-on-budget-as-mom-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753181701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687b9d8