%20or%20haven't%20prepared%20anything%20to%20ask.%20That's%20why%2C%20after%20years%20of%20conducting%20interviews%2C%20he%20often%20starts%20by%20asking%20candidates%20to%20go%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20questions%20are%20a%20huge%20tell%2C%26quot%3B%20Lambros%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20candidates'%20answers%20often%20signal%20what%20they%20think%20about%20the%20opportunity%20and%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20speaks%20to%20just%20their%20level%20of%20interest%2C%20their%20level%20of%20engagement%2C%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20Lambros%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bhow%20good%20they%20would%20be%20on%20the%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20came%20to%20this%20method%20early%20in%20his%20career%2C%20he%20said%2C%20after%20reading%20various%20books%20on%20sales%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0thinking%20of%20an%20interview%20more%20like%20a%20discovery%20call.%20Lambros%20estimates%20that%20he's%20sat%20down%20with%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELambros%20is%20now%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmeetdex.ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDex%2C%20a%20recruiting%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20talent%20agent%20and%20connect%20software%20engineers%20with%20employers.%20The%20London%20startup's%20backers%20include%20A16z%20Speedrun%2C%20the%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20accelerator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aff006a0-e4d8-4270-9a53-34c608f3d54b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESigns%20of%20a%20top%20performer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20Lambros%20prefers%20not%20to%20wait%20until%20the%20end%20to%20have%20interviewees%20ask%20questions%20is%20that%20it's%20now%20common%2C%20he%20said%2C%20for%20candidates%20to%20turn%20up%20with%20%26quot%3Bincredibly%20groomed%20answers%20that%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-appreciation-day-chatgpt-snark-202