Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvancouver-travel-mistakes-to-avoid-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBritish%20Columbia%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20years%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flived-in-major-us-cities-went-back-to-hometown-rochester-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20big%20cities%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20we%20were%20craving%20something%20different.%20We%20wanted%20our%20kids%20(at%20the%20time%2C%20we%20had%20a%202-year-old%20and%20a%20newborn)%20to%20grow%20up%20with%20space%20to%20roam%2C%20clean%20air%20to%20breathe%2C%20and%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20community.%20We%20dreamed%20of%20a%20slower%20pace%2C%20afternoon%20bike%20rides%20to%20the%20lake%2C%20and%20winters%20spent%20skiing%20instead%20of%20commuting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20that%20dream%20came%20true.%20But%20what%20we%20didn't%20fully%20grasp%20was%20what%20we'd%20be%20giving%20up%2C%20which%20was%20the%20consistent%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdecided-raise-kids-family-near-grandparents-pros-and-cons-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresence%20of%20grandparents%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20reliable%20network%20of%20support%20that%20only%20close%20family%20can%20provide.%20We%20underestimated%20the%20emotional%20weight%20of%20raising%20kids%20without%20our%20parents%20nearby%20and%20how%20much%20they%20would%20miss%20being%20part%20of%20our%20children's%20daily%20lives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221df4e9b5-425f-4ed0-b10f-c3e19b4c7682%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20lifestyle%20trade-off%20felt%20worth%20it%20at%20first%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoving%20to%20Nelson%20from%20a%20major%20city%20was%20a%20major%20lifestyle%20upgrade.%20The%20lake%20views%20are%20stunning%2C%20there%20are%20hiking%20trails%20minutes%20from%20our%20front%20door%2C%20and%20we%20have%20a%20tight-knit%2C%20creative%20community%20that%20rallies%20around%20its%20kids.%20Our%20children%20have%20the%20kind%20of%20freedom%20I%20was%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20have%20as%20a%20suburban%20kid%2C%20such%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-shares-benefits-biking-around-with-kids-instead-of-driving-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eriding%20bikes%20to%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20building%20forts%20in%20the%20woods%2C%20and%20learning%20to%20ski%20on%20weekends.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20to%20mention%2C%20we're%20more%20active%2C%20more%20present%2C%20and%20more%20connected%20to%20nature%20than%20we%20ever%20were%20in%20the%20city.%20We've%20cultivated%20a%20sense%20of%20spaciousness%20and%20calmness%20in%20our%20days%20that's%20hard%20to%20describe%20until%20you've%20lived%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20move%20here%20wasn't%20made%20lightly.%20We%20considered%20the%20lengthy%20drive%20to%20see%20family%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20direct%20flights%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20winter%20travel%20in%20the%20mountains%20can%20be%20perilous%20at%20the%20best%20of%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20we%20told%20ourselves%20we'd%20visit%20often.%20We%20assumed%20the%20bond%20between%20our%20kids%20and%20their%20grandparents%20would%20remain%20strong%2C%20even%20with%20the%20miles%20between%20us.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a28d377-db9e-46ed-b646-1a0d6940004f%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20absence%20of%20family%20ran%20deeper%20than%20we%20expected%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-no-grandparents-void-community-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELong-distance%20grandparenting%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20hard%20for%20everyone%20involved%2C%20including%20my%20partner%20and%20me.%20We%20miss%20the%20impromptu%20dinners%2C%20the%20free%20babysitting%2C%20the%20help%20when%20one%20of%20the%20kids%20is%20sick%2C%20and%20we%20both%20have%20pressing%20deadlines.%20But%20more%20than%20anything%2C%20we%20miss%20the%20presence%20of%20people%20who%20love%20our%20children%20as%20much%20as%20we%20do.%20That%20kind%20of%20love%20is%20irreplaceable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20been%20especially%20hard%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstaying-present-no-kids-parents-getting-older-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewatch%20my%20parents%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20a%20distance.%20With%20each%20visit%2C%20I%20feel%20the%20dull%20ache%20of%20time%20slipping%20by.%20I%20notice%20subtle%20changes%2C%20like%20slower%20movement%20and%20more%20forgetfulness.%20I%20think%20about%20all%20the%20ordinary%20moments%20our%20kids%20don't%20get%20to%20share%20with%20them%3A%20baking%20cookies%2C%20reading%20books%2C%20getting%20picked%20up%20from%20school%20%26quot%3Bjust%20because.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20parents%20try.%20They%20video%20chat%2C%20they%20send%20cards%20in%20the%20mail%2C%20and%20they%20make%20the%20seven-hour%20drive%20a%20few%20times%20a%20year.%20But%20it's%20not%20the%20same%20as%20watching%20your%20grandkids%20grow%20up%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243d199a8-364d-44fa-9a43-9eb51b6d8793%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe've%20had%20to%20get%20creative%20to%20stay%20connected%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20help%20bridge%20the%20gap%2C%20we've%20established%20some%20rituals%2C%20like%20Saturday%20morning%20FaceTime%20calls%2C%20monthly%20mail%20swaps%20(our%20kids%20love%20sending%20their%20drawings)%2C%20and%20using%20those%20digital%20photo%20frames%20that%20you%20can%20upload%20photos%20to%20from%20an%20app.%20Now%20that%20our%20kids%20are%208%20and%2010%2C%20we%20can%20meet%20our%20parents%20halfway%20between%20our%20homes%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrandparents-babysat-hotel-during-wedding-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20them%20take%20the%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20a%20week%20or%20two%20without%20my%20partner%20and%20me%20being%20there.%20It's%20times%20like%20these%20that%20their%20bond%20truly%20flourishes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20rituals%20help.%20But%20some%20days%2C%20it%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20enough.%20I%20often%20wonder%20if%20we%20made%20the%20right%20decision%20moving%20far%20away.%20Did%20we%20choose%20adventure%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20closeness%3F%20Are%20we%20giving%20our%20kids%20a%20magical%20childhood%2C%20or%20robbing%20them%20of%20deeper%20relationships%3F%20Maybe%20the%20answer%20is%20both.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20I%20do%20know%20is%20that%20we%20made%20this%20move%20out%20of%20love.%20We%20wanted%20to%20raise%20our%20kids%20in%20a%20place%20that%20reflects%20our%20values%20of%20community%2C%20nature%2C%20and%20togetherness.%20But%20I've%20learned%20that%20%26quot%3Btogetherness%26quot%3B%20isn't%20just%20about%20where%20you%20live.%20It's%20about%20who%20you%20let%20in%20and%20how%20you%20find%20ways%20to%20show%20up%20for%20each%20other%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20far%20apart%20you%20live.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-move-mountain-town-away-from-grandparents-struggle-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753178882000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687e76fd85e81483682e5f86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-move-mountain-town-away-from-grandparents-struggle-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20family%20of%204%20moved%20to%20a%20quiet%20mountain%20town%20and%20it%20was%20a%20major