k-promises-40m-in-aid-13399832%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20Hour%20From%20Mumbai%2C%20This%20Family%20Built%20a%203-Acre%20Forest%20Stay%20With%20800%2B%20Trees%20%26amp%3B%20140%20Plant%20Varieties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20of%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20stretch%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20atmosphere%20at%20The%20Chlorophyll%20Estate%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F298395%2Fmohraan-farmstay-in-thane-offers-kayaking-natural-pools-food-forest-adventure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20farm%20stay%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Mumbai%20%E2%80%94%20could%20be%20an%20antidote%20to%20the%20chaos%20of%20the%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20would%20swear%20that%20time%20ticks%20at%20a%20slower%20pace%20here%2C%20and%20the%20sky%20is%20definitely%20a%20brighter%20blue.%20That%20this%20place%20%E2%80%94%20with%20its%20fields%20of%20Italian%20basil%2C%20mulberries%2C%20stevia%2C%20and%20rose%20apples%20%E2%80%94%20is%20just%20an%20hour%E2%80%99s%20drive%20from%20the%20big%20city%20is%20almost%20unbelievable.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289450%2Fmumbai-couple-make-eco-friendly-farm-stay-in-nashik-with-mud-tiles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThis%20transformation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20not%20an%20overnight%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20points%20out%20Keyur%20Barad%20(38)%20and%20one-half%20of%20the%20entrepreneur%20brother%20duo%20who%20spearheaded%20this%20project.%20He%20clarifies%20that%20it%20took%20him%20and%20his%20brother%20Nishit%20(41)%2015%20long%20years%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctoil%2C%20sweat%2C%20time%2C%20savings%20and%20sheer%20perseverance%E2%80%9D%20to%20create%20this.%